Simple and easy to use, but powerfull and accurate tool to quickly find the size of your jewelry ring. With this app you can:

- choose between metric and imperial units
- choose diameter or circumference
- use unique visual guides for precise measuring
- easily share your ring size through email and social networks
- use up to seven different ring size measure systems, including USA, 
  Canada, Australia, Great Britain, Europe, Italy, Spain, Germany, Russia,
  Japan, China, India, Hong Kong and Brazil.

Ring sizer pro supports a very wide diapason of the possible sizes. From 0000 to 16 in USA size system.

Some of the countries share the same measure system. For example USA system is also used in Canada and Mexico. If you don't find you country in the preferences try to find which country use the same system.

If you find any mistakes in the measure in you country please send me a letter and I will fix issue in the next app update. Thank you!

The app does not require users to create any login account.
